data.installInstructions:
aws --profile deltagene s3 cp s3://bb-tools-installers/trimmomatic/trimmomatic-0.36.tar.gz /home/ec2-user/trimmomatic-0.36.tar.gz
mkdir -p /home/ec2-user/trimmomatic-0.36
tar -zxvf trimmomatic-0.36.tar.gz -C /home/ec2-user/trimmomatic-0.36
ln -s /home/ec2-user/trimmomatic-0.36 /trimmomatic || true
ln -s /trimmomatic/trimmomatic-0.36.jar /trimmomatic/trimmomatic || true
data.name: trimmomatic

data.installInstructions:
aws --profile deltagene s3 cp s3://bb-tools-installers/fastqc/FastQC.tar.gz /home/ec2-user/FastQC.tar.gz
tar -zxvf FastQC.tar.gz -C /usr/lib
chmod 755 /usr/lib/FastQC/fastqc
ln -s /usr/lib/FastQC/fastqc /bin/fastqc
data.name: fastqc
